<h3>Newsletter popup</h3>
<p class="indent">The given module allows to display a pop-up block with the newsletter subscription form.<br>
You can enable/disable the module via Magento Admin Panel in <strong>System > Configuration > Templatemonster > NewsletterPopup</strong> section.</p>
<figure class="img-polaroid"><img src="img/magento/newsletter.jpg" alt="" /></figure>
<p class="indent">In order to edit the appearance of the window, you need to edit the <strong>style.css</strong> file of the theme. If you need to add several user elements to the pop-up block, you need to edit the <strong>newsletterpopup.phtml</strong> file located in the <strong>app/design/frontend/default/themeXXX/template/tm/newsletterpopup</strong> folder.</p>
		